      <title>Dish Network 与投资者谈判以和解诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/dish-network-in-talks-with-investors-to-settle-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Dish Network Corp. 是一家陷入困境的卫星电视提供商，负债超过 200 亿美元，目前正在与一群债权人进行谈判，以解决与有争议的资产转移有关的诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/dish-network-in-talks-with-investors-to-settle-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:24:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国针对中国实施新的量子、芯片相关出口限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/us-targets-china-with-new-quantum-chip-related-export-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府正在对包括量子计算和半导体产品在内的关键技术实施新的出口管制，使美国与盟友结盟，共同阻止中国和其他敌对国家的进步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/us-targets-china-with-new-quantum-chip-related-export-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:58:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
