      <title>美国银行称英伟达股价暴跌为买入提供了诱人的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/nvidia-s-rout-makes-for-compelling-chance-to-buy-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行表示，人工智能宠儿英伟达公司近期面临阻力，但这种阻力使其估值显得颇具吸引力，为投资者提供了颇具吸引力的买入机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/nvidia-s-rout-makes-for-compelling-chance-to-buy-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首次公开募股后，Ardian 将退出 Planisware 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/ardian-moves-to-exit-planisware-stake-following-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[收购集团 Ardian 正考虑出售其在 Planisware SA 的剩余股份，该集团从这家法国软件公司今年早些时候首次公开募股以来股价上涨中获利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/ardian-moves-to-exit-planisware-stake-following-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:21:12 GMT</pubDate>
